<article class="page-container">
    <form  class="form form-horizontal" id="form-attendconference-add">
        <input type="hidden" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="confId" name="confId">

        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>会议名称：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="conferenceName" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>论文题目：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="paperTitle" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-3">举办时间：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8">
                <input type="text" onfocus="WdatePicker({ maxDate:'#F{$dp.$D(\'datemax\')||\'%y-%M-%d\'}' })" id="time"
                       class="input-text Wdate" style="width:120px;">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>地点：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="place" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>主办单位：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="hostUnit" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-3">会议类别：</label>
            <div class="formControls skin-minimal col-xs-5">
                <div class="radio-box">
                    <input type="radio" id="cat1" name="conferenceCategory" value="国际学术会议">
                    <label for="cat1">国际学术会议</label>
                </div>
                <div class="radio-box">
                    <input type="radio" id="cat2" name="conferenceCategory" value="港澳台学术会议">
                    <label for="cat2">港澳台学术会议</label>
                </div>
                <div class="radio-box">
                    <input type="radio" id="cat2" name="conferenceCategory" value="国内学术会议">
                    <label for="cat3">国内学术会议</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3">证明附件：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9"> <span class="btn-upload form-group">
                <input class="input-text upload-url" type="text" name="uploadfile" id="uploadfile" readonly nullmsg="请添加附件！" style="width:200px">
                <a href="javascript:void();" class="btn btn-primary radius upload-btn"><i class="Hui-iconfont">&#xe642;</i> 浏览文件</a>
                <input type="file" multiple id="file" name="file" class="input-file">
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-9 col-xs-offset-4 col-sm-offset-3">
                <input class="btn btn-primary radius" id="submit" type="button" value="&nbsp;&nbsp;修改&nbsp;&nbsp;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div class="text-shadow">
        <p>注意：</p>
        <p>不重新上传默认用上一次提交的附件。重新上传则覆盖</p>
        <p>说明：会议类别分为</p>
        <p>（1）“国际学术会议”指有两个及以上国家的专家学者参加的学术会议，不管在哪举行；</p>
        <p>（2）“港澳台学术会议”指有大陆和港澳台地区专家学者参加，但没有其他国家专家学者参加的学术会议；</p>
        <p>（3）“国内学术会议”指在国内举行，且只有本国专家学者参加的学术会议（含全国性、地区性）；</p>
    </div>

</article>

